          <heading>Section 352-15</heading>
          <content>
            <p>§352-15  Recreational and program
activities.
The director shall provide the opportunity for the recreation
of those persons committed to the facilities.  Work programs for such persons
shall be established and may include farming, sewing, plant nursery, and animal
husbandry. [L 1980, c 303, pt of §8(1)]
